channel.title: MyFax Channel
channel.description:
FaxCompare.com was created to consolidate and organize information about the top providers of efax services so that you can make an "apples to apples" comparison of the different service providers and select the one that best fits your needs.
This recording is an interview between Mr. Gaines Kilpatrick, a FaxCompare.com CEO, and Steve Adams, a MyFax representative. This interview consists of a series of questions about efax services, how they work, and what MyFax does to meet its customers' needs.

item.title: Zilker Ventures, LLC interviews Internet fax leader, MyFax
item.description: Gaines Kilpatrick of Zilker Ventures, LLC recently sat down with Steve Adams of Internet fax leader MyFax, to ask 20 questions about the present and future of MyFax and the Internet fax industry in general. Adams describes the world of Internet fax and speaks about assuaging fax machine users' fears about online faxing.
